  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.apng?t=1740693230\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.poster.avif?t=1740693230\" class=\"bb_img\" width=48 height=48 /></picture></span><br><strong><br>UNIQUE GAMES EVERY TIME</strong><br>The game features a random map system, including the generation of various types of trees, rocks, bushes, and animals with each new game, each with its own specific attributes, making every game unique.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.apng?t=1740693230\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.poster.avif?t=1740693230\" class=\"bb_img\" width=48 height=48 /></picture></span><br><strong>BUILD</strong><br>There are various types of buildings available in the game, from houses, fishing traps, fences, and plantations to different types of flooring.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.apng?t=1740693230\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.poster.avif?t=1740693230\" class=\"bb_img\" width=48 height=48 /></picture></span><br><strong>PLANTATIONS</strong><br>Various types of plantations are available.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.apng?t=1740693230\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.poster.avif?t=1740693230\" class=\"bb_img\" width=48 height=48 /></picture></span><br><strong>FACE THE ENVIRONMENT</strong><br>The game has weather changes that affect the player's gameplay, such as rain. In addition, there are wild animals that can harm the village, from wolves to birds.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.apng?t=1740693230\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.poster.avif?t=1740693230\" class=\"bb_img\" width=48 height=48 /></picture></span><br><strong>A NEW RTS SYSTEM</strong><br>The game features a new system for controlling villagers, where the player does not directly control the villager but selects only the type of resource to be collected. The villager has the autonomy to choose which resource to collect, making the game more dynamic.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.apng?t=1740693230\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133140/extras/ae18b2ec02e44589fd8368ec5a00d4d8.poster.avif?t=1740693230\" class=\"bb_img\" width=48 height=48 /></picture></span><br><strong>FISH, FISH, AND FISH!</strong><br>The game features 100 different species of fish for the player to catch!",
